{"tid":112192,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"61歲李兆基已經中風兩年","createTime":"2017-02-08T03:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T10:54:15.000Z","uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c97c99d05004485a2b17c69e689c4ea3d766e16","tid":112192,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1u40WH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1u40WH.jpg&h=a5919ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靠惡起家的李兆基基哥，近兩年甚少在幕前演出，原來他不幸中風。日前壹仔在九龍城發現基哥吃下午茶，瘦了不少的他，眼神依然保持凌厲。不過他的半邊身似乎不太夠力，所以要靠拐杖借力，而且還行得比較慢。<br />\n<br />\n記者上前做訪問，惡人原來得個樣。他說：「輕微中風，人老了沒辦法。都兩年了。」問到他生活可成問題？他竟不忌諱道：「我現在沒環境沒入息，我一班老友久不久給我錢。可能我是古惑仔出身，娛樂圈的人都不比古惑仔好，是真的，現在找我吃飯的、給錢我的都是以前的古惑仔兄弟。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20170208/476502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20170208%2F476502&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9ONr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3f911124\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20170208%2F476502&h=a270e3b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20170208/476502</a>"},{"pid":"74c38c68421fa54dcc18280706537ab4adcb6a0b","tid":112192,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c82af0f8658214551325a9deef153ca5bdf603","tid":112192,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60429ef03c15327bed60c11f7a29ddd4d7811332","tid":112192,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"殘左咁多！"},{"pid":"d2fbb36cafc8f372dd07ddf7f042322bc0952c90","tid":112192,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T0